What is flutter?
A tool/framework that allows to build native cross-platform(ios + Android) apps with one build with one codebase with same programming language

React_Native is also a cross flatform

01. Framework / Widget Library 
    to buid ui design

02. SDK - Software Deevelopment Kit
    uso compile e to native machine code


